T02TD3077E:172b-0: @172b sangs rgyas kyi sku dang mchod rten gyi cha dbye ba bshad pa /
T02TD3077E:172b-1: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed thams cad kyi sku ni rnam pa gnyis te /
T02TD3077E:172b-4: de la tshe blangs pa'i sku ni yab yum las skyes pa'i mig dang yid tshim par byed pa /
T02TD3077E:172b-5: dag par byed pa skrun par byed pa sta /
T02TD3077E:172b-6: sku tshigs re re zhing sred med kyi bu'i stobs dang ldan la /
T02TD3077E:172b-7: tshigs re re yang bsod nams brgya'i mtshan gyis brgyan pa dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-8: skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis brgyan zhing dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus mdzes par byas pa mthong na ba lta bas chog mi shes shing mi mthun pa med pa dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-9: blta bar bya ba bla na med pa ni bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi tshe blangs pa'i sku'o //
T02TD3077E:172b-10: de bzhin gshegs pa dag bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku ni /
T02TD3077E:172b-11: bcom ldan 'das kyis sangs rgyas kyi ye shes kyis thugs su chud par zad kyi /
T02TD3077E:172b-12: rang sangs rgyas bse ru lta bu dag dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-13: gnas brtan sh'a ri'i bu la sogs pa nyan thos chen po rnams nam chad ni /
T02TD3077E:172b-14: su yang rgya chen yang dag par rab tu ston par ji ltar byas kyang nus pa med de /
T02TD3077E:172b-16: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa bzhi dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-17: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-20: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-21: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa ste /
T02TD3077E:172b-22: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun po'i chos 'di dag dang /
T02TD3077E:172b-24: dge sbyong gi 'bras bu bzhi dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-3: so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-7: bsrung ba med pa gsum dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-9: bsod nams bya ba'i dngos po gsum dang ;
T02TD3077E:173a-10: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-11: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-12: zil gyis gnon pa'i skye mched brgyad dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-13: mthar gyi gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-14: zad par gyi skye mched bcu dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-15: mi slob pa'i chos bcu dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-16: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-17: gnas dang gnas ma yin pa mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-18: las bdag gis bya ba mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-23: dbang po mchog dang mchog ma yin pa mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-24: mos pa sna tshogs mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-25: khams sna tshogs mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-26: thams cad du 'gro ba'i lam mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-27: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-28: 'chi 'pho dang skye ba mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-29: zag pa zad par mkhyen pa'i stobs so //
T02TD3077E:173a-30: ma 'dres pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gsum dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-31: mngon par shes pa drug dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-32: rtag tu gnas par bya ba drug dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-33: ma 'dres par bsgom pa rnams dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-35: nyon mongs pa med pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa rnams dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-37: shes rab kyi mthar phyin pa dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-45: 'jig rten gyi chos kyi mchog dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-49: rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba yan lag bcu gnyis dang /
T02TD3077E:173a-53: dbang po nyi shu gnyis rnams yin no //
T02TD3077E:173b-0: zab cing mchog tu zab pa'i chos 'di dag ni yang dag par rdzogs @173b pa'i sangs rgyas gangg'a'i klung gi bye ma snyed kyis gsungs pa ste /
T02TD3077E:173b-1: gang rang rang gi mtshan nyid dang /
T02TD3077E:173b-2: spyi'i mtshan nyid rjes su rtogs nas nyid kyis thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thugs su chud de /
T02TD3077E:173b-7: mu stegs can sna tshogs dge sbyong dang /
T02TD3077E:173b-18: lto 'phye chen po rnams la rgya cher yang dag par rab tu bstan te /
T02TD3077E:173b-19: sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba rnams btul nas 'khor grangs med pa khrag khrig brgya stong dang /
T02TD3077E:173b-20: mya ngan las 'das pa 'jigs pa med pa'i grong khyer du zhugs so //
T02TD3077E:173b-21: sangs rgyas kyi sku bshad pa rdzogs so//
